Paper: hep-th/0212129

Date: 2002-12-11

Title: Invariance quantum group of the fermionic oscillator

Authors: M. Arik, S. Gun, A. Yildiz

Comments: 7 A4 pages

The fermionic oscillator defined by the algebraic relations cc^*+c^*c=1 andc^{2}=0 admits the homogeneous group O(2) as its invariance group. We showthat, the structure of the inhomogeneous invariance group of this oscillator isa quantum group.